---
layout: post
title: Recover a deleted entry in the Mac app 
description: Day One的误删除恢复  
keywords: OsX,Day One  
---  
  
  

-------------

Day One 是woodjuice在 Macbook Pro 上记录流水日记的一个常用 APP，今天手贱误删除了一篇日志，却没有 找到Trash，也没有找到恢复的办法。查看了[官方 help 文档](https://dayone.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/200714674-Recover-a-deleted-entry-in-the-Mac-app)，才找到恢复的办法。  

官方提供了两种办法，分别应对两种情况：  
  
### A. Undo 可以生效的时候，在 `Edit` 菜单使用 `Undo`。  

> 
If the entry is still open and you have not yet tapped Done:  tap Edit in the Mac menu bar, then tap Undo.  


>If you have already tapped 'Done' to exit the entry: there is unfortunately no way to recover the deleted text.   


即：删除完未点击` Done `按钮，这时候可以用 `Undo`。

### B. Undo不可用的时候。  

>
Open the Trash folder in a Finder window, and look for a file with the .doentry extension. The full filename will be something like this:  


>E1FE50B7B57A4BBDB79233105403CBBA.doentry  
  

>Right-click on that file, then open it with TextEdit. In the file that opens, you will see a lot of unintelligible meta-data; the actual text of your entry will appear intact in the middle of the meta-data.  Locate the text, copy it, and paste it into a new entry in Day One.
```

即：去系统的 trash 里找到以`.doentry`为后缀的文件，用文本编辑器打开，然后复制黏贴到新的日志里。事实上在 txt 里可以看到其文件是 符合html的。  

**如果连系统回收站都已经被清空了，那只能去 Dropbox 或者 icloud 之类同步的地方去碰碰运气了。**  

忙活了半天的键盘侠表示：这真是一个悲伤的故事...

Reference: https://dayone.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/200714674-Recover-a-deleted-entry-in-the-Mac-app